description:
This canyon is described in comprehensive detail in Canyoning Around Victoria guidebook


Approach

Park your car at the end of the fire trail described in detail in the guidebook. An AWD is recommended although you may be able to get there in a 2WD depending on it's clearance. It's not necessary to have high clearance.

Walk from the trailhead on the fire trail to Big Talbingo just after the telecommunications structures.
